<article class="post--single post-500 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorized tag-brian-w-ferry tag-friendship tag-london tag-london-is-the-place-for-me tag-photography tag-st-john tag-towpath tag-travel" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
