    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The Scottish countryside is seriously lovely this time of year, as long as you don&#39;t mind the rain. I loved getting up in the morning, hearing the rain patter on the skylight, only to look out behind me and see a few bobbing heads of horses in their paddock, absolutely enveloped by the fog. The fog! It&#39;s only comparable to that of Ireland, another favorite of mine. I am seriously swooning at the thought of your spontaneous adventure to come! Enjoy! Take lots of photos!</p>
    </div>

