      <p>Edinburgh is such a moody, magical place.  I&#39;ll never forget arriving for the first time,at night,and coming up out of bowels of the train station to see the castle on its rocky cragg all lit up.  When I lived there I loved to go to Patisserie Florentin and get a cafe au lait and some very pretty pastry and people watch.  Enjoy it!</p>
