    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>We lived in Edinburgh for two-and-a-half years before we made the leap across the pond.  Please make sure to visit the legendary deli Valvona &#038; Crolla on Elm Row.  I&#39;d make you go to Plaisir du Chocolat too, if it hadn&#39;t &#8211; very sadly &#8211; closed down.  Also, if you can spare a train ride to Glasgow, be sure to stop in at Voltaire &#038; Rousseau.  It&#39;s the sort of used bookstore dreams are made of.  </p>
<p>You will have a magical stay.</p>
