      <p>I think madeleines can cure just about anything. A friend just sent me an article about the power of madeleines (and other delicious french treats) in a small town in New Hampshire. <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/01/us/01land.html?pagewanted=all" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/01/us/01land.html?pagewanted=all</a></p>
<p>Both you and this little town are making happy endings. So lovely!</p>
    </div>

