  <li id="comment-27240" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/10/october-14/#comment-27240"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-10-20T21:37:32-04:00">Thursday, October 20, 2011 at 9:37 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I hope you can make it up to Scotland&#8230; Edinburgh is an amazing city, beautiful, breathtaking, deep.<br />You may also want to go up to Dunnotar castle ruins, near the small town of Stonehaven, which is a short busride up the Eastern coast from Edinburgh.. where you may see a lone seal swimming in the shallow waters near the shore, as I did.  My friend and I found some ripe strawberries, crusty bread and a nice white wine in the town nearby and made a meal of that while on the hike to the ruins.</p>
    </div>

